00:10:42,059 --> 00:10:43,039
Look

297
00:10:43,779 --> 00:10:45,779
Dad will just sit here and keep you company for a while

298
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:48,840
Dad can do anything for you

299
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,980
How about Dad becomes your assistant

300
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:55,639
That way I can take care of you every day

301
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:58,120
Do you know how to be an assistant

302
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:58,840
Well

303
