305
00:11:03,139 --> 00:11:04,399
Serving tea, pouring water, and cooking

306
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,899
Massaging the boss's shoulders when free

307
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:08,399
Then what am I supposed to do

308
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:10,580
You may look ugly

309
00:11:11,299 --> 00:11:12,980
but you sure dream big

310
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:14,000
Bai Fengqin

311
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,379
No

312
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,539
Why is she here

313
00:11:16,139 --> 00:11:18,500
The daughter I raised with so much hardship

314
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:20,740
Why shouldn't I come

315
00:11:20,779 --> 00:11:22,539
As for you, Liang

316
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,440
Please

317
00:11:24,019 --> 00:11:25,240
stay away

318
00:11:25,539 --> 00:11:26,340
from my daughter

319
00:11:27,039 --> 00:11:27,980
Who is this

320
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:28,659
You two

321
00:11:28,659 --> 00:11:31,259
Stop filming

322
00:11:31,419 --> 00:11:32,299
Stop filming

323
00:11:33,039 --> 00:11:33,779
Change

324
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:36,440
"with the assistance of comrades"

325
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:37,440
to

326
00:11:38,139 --> 00:11:39,200
"all by myself"

327
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,340
"single-handedly"

328
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,799
"All by myself, single-handedly"

329
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:42,639
Right, good

330
00:11:42,879 --> 00:11:44,080
Still writing

331
00:11:44,899 --> 00:11:46,519
Can't you spare the kid

332
00:11:46,679 --> 00:11:47,820
Then you type for me

333
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,019
Let me take a look first

334
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,840
How's the writing going

335
00:11:54,580 --> 00:11:55,179
Old Li

336
00:11:55,340 --> 00:11:56,500
Listen to this paragraph

337
00:11:57,440 --> 00:12:00,059
It was May Day, 1980

338
00:12:00,519 --> 00:12:03,480
My fiancée and I went on our first date

339
00:12:05,539 --> 00:12:08,100
We watched the movie *Shaolin Temple*

340
00:12:09,059 --> 00:12:11,259
It was truly an unforgettable night

341
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,179
How is it

342
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:13,899
Jealous, aren't you

343
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:16,179
Fed you a mouthful of dog food

344
00:12:16,299 --> 00:12:17,759
Pah, you're the dog

345
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:18,740
Dog brain

346
00:12:19,059 --> 00:12:19,820
*Shaolin Temple*

347
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:20,899
What year was it released

348
00:12:21,179 --> 00:12:21,840
1980

349
00:12:21,899 --> 00:12:22,379
Wrong

350
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,399
It was '82, okay

351
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:25,720
Right

352
