I checked

354
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:30,320
*Shaolin Temple* really was released in 1982

355
00:12:30,440 --> 00:12:31,379
See

356
00:12:32,799 --> 00:12:33,919
Listen to this part of yours again

357
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:38,500
The poem she loved

358
00:12:38,659 --> 00:12:40,120
I wrote in the love letter

359
00:12:40,639 --> 00:12:43,879
The most memorable was Xu Zhimo's *Fragment*

360
00:12:45,620 --> 00:12:46,419
You

361
00:12:46,740 --> 00:12:49,419
stand on the bridge viewing the scenery

362
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:50,840
Never heard of this poem

363
00:12:51,899 --> 00:12:52,580
Classy, right

364
